How to build and run the applications:

serial:
> cd serial
> make
> ./serial [...]
Use argument -h for further instructions on running.

pthreads:
> cd pthreads
> make
> ./pthreads [...]
Use argument -h for further instructions on running.

openmp
> cd openmp
> make
> ./openmp [...]
Use argument -h for further instructions on running.

mpi:
> cd mpi
> make
> chmod +x run.sh
> ./run.sh [n_proc] [...]
Where n_proc is the number of processors to use.
Use argument -h for further instructions on running.